{"article_id":"aDkDRiBmFbcgAar6","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Justices Struggle","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"To Find Line Between Threats , Free Speech Online","depth":2},{"id":2,"text":"The U.S. Supreme Court struggled Monday with conflicting notions","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"of where to draw the line between free speech and criminal threats in the Internet age .","depth":4},{"id":4,"text":"At issue was the conviction of a Pennsylvania man","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"for making threats against his estranged wife and an FBI agent .","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"After Anthony Elonis ' wife left him ,","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"he began posting grisly messages on his Facebook page ,","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"promising not to rest","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"until her body was `` soaked in blood","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"and dying . ''","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"She then got a court order","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"barring him from threatening and harassing her , even indirectly .","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"But he continued to post on Facebook ,","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"asking","depth":11},{"id":15,"text":"if the court order was `` thick enough","depth":12},{"id":16,"text":"to stop a bullet ''","depth":12},{"id":17,"text":"and musing about making a name for himself","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"by shooting up a kindergarten .","depth":11},{"id":19,"text":"After a visit from a female FBI agent , he posted on Facebook ,","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"saying","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"it `` took all the strength","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"I had","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"not to ... slit her throat ,","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"leave her bleedin ' from her jugular . ''","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"Elonis was convicted of making illegal threats","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"and sentenced to 44 months in prison .","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"But he contends","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"that he is an aspiring rap artist ,","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"and that his comments were just his way","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"of venting and expressing himself .","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"The case has become a test of what the prosecution must prove","depth":4},{"id":32,"text":"to win a conviction in Internet threat cases .","depth":4},{"id":33,"text":"The government ,","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"backed by victims ' rights groups ,","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"contends","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"that the prosecution must show only that a reasonable person would interpret the Facebook posts as threats","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"to commit bodily harm .","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"But Elonis ' lawyer , John Elwood , told the court","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"that the prosecution must make a far more rigorous showing .","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"`` How does one prove what 's in somebody else 's mind ? ''","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"asked Justice Ruth Bader Ginsburg ,","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"who was back on the bench","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"just five days after having a heart stent implanted .","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"Elwood answered","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"that you can examine a person 's computer and cellphone records .","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"`` Yeah , you are going to find a lot of information on the cellphone","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"that the guy is really angry at his ex-wife","depth":13},{"id":48,"text":"and would like her to suffer , ''","depth":13},{"id":49,"text":"Chief Justice John Roberts observed ,","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"and","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"when he puts some of that online ,","depth":12},{"id":52,"text":"he 's going to claim","depth":13},{"id":53,"text":"that the post was `` therapeutic '' venting .","depth":13},{"id":54,"text":"`` I 'm trying to figure out what 'level of intent ' you want , ''","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"Justice Elena Kagan said to lawyer Elwood .","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"The highest level ,","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"she noted ,","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"would require proof","depth":12},{"id":59,"text":"that the purpose was to put `` this person in fear . '' A step down would be that `` I know","depth":14},{"id":60,"text":"that I am going to place this person in fear , ''","depth":14},{"id":61,"text":"but I am `` fulfilling my artistic fantasies . ''","depth":13},{"id":62,"text":"And a third level would be recklessness ,","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"meaning","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"that `` you know","depth":14},{"id":65,"text":"there is a substantial probability","depth":15},{"id":66,"text":"that you will place that person in fear , ''","depth":15},{"id":67,"text":"but you do n't know it `` to a certainty . ''","depth":13},{"id":68,"text":"Elwood picked the second option , knowledge","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"that you would put someone in fear .","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"`` What would be wrong with a recklessness standard ? ''","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"Kagan asked .","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"`` It gets you up one level from what the government wants . ''","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"Elwood argued","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"that it would allow people , many of them teenagers ,","depth":12},{"id":75,"text":"who are just `` shooting off their mouths , ''","depth":12},{"id":76,"text":"to be thrown in jail .","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"Justice Samuel Alito , however , countered","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"that Elwood 's standard would provide `` a road map","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"for threatening a spouse","depth":12},{"id":80,"text":"and getting away with it .","depth":12},{"id":81,"text":"'' You would only have to say `` just kidding '' at the end of a post ,","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"or call yourself `` an aspiring rap artist , ''","depth":12},{"id":83,"text":"he said .","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"When Elonis threatened to shoot up a kindergarten ,","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"Justice Alito added ,","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"would the jury have to `` get into the mind of this obsessed , somewhat disturbed individual ''","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"and try to figure out","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"whether he really knew","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"that this would cause a panic on the part of the school officials and parents ? `","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"` Yes , exactly , ''","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"Elwood said.","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"`` It 's the same thing","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"that juries do all the time . ''","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"Arguing the contrary position ,","depth":7},{"id":95,"text":"Deputy Solicitor General Michael Dreeben contended","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"that people like Elonis should be held accountable for the `` ordinary and natural meaning of the words ''","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"they use , in context .","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"Chief Justice Roberts , the father of teenagers , asked","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"if the reasonable person standard would also mean a reasonable teenager .","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"What about an older audience ?","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"Would the person","depth":12},{"id":102,"text":"posting on Facebook","depth":12},{"id":103,"text":"have to know","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"how rap lyrics are interpreted by a `` general audience ? ''","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"Roberts then read aloud some explicit lyrics from rapper Eminem about what he would like to do to his ex-wife .","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"Would those words justify prosecution ,","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"asked the chief justice .","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"No ,","depth":11},{"id":109,"text":"Dreeben replied ,","depth":11},{"id":110,"text":"because Eminem 's lyrics are said `` at a concert","depth":11},{"id":111,"text":"where people are going to be entertained . ''","depth":11},{"id":112,"text":"The critical context here is that Eminem did n't voice his lyrics privately ,","depth":11},{"id":113,"text":"said Dreeben ,","depth":11},{"id":114,"text":"nor had the rapper 's wife gotten a protection-from-abuse order .","depth":10},{"id":115,"text":"Justice Stephen Breyer ,","depth":9},{"id":116,"text":"noting","depth":10},{"id":117,"text":"that a lot of these threat cases arise in domestic relations matters ,","depth":10},{"id":118,"text":"observed","depth":8},{"id":119,"text":"that `` people do say things in domestic disputes","depth":8},{"id":120,"text":"that they are awfully sorry about later . ''","depth":8},{"id":121,"text":"Justice Antonin Scalia took issue with that proposition .","depth":9},{"id":122,"text":"`` I do n't agree ...","depth":11},{"id":123,"text":"that in marital disputes people make physical threats ...","depth":11},{"id":124,"text":"I think","depth":11},{"id":125,"text":"that 's rather unusual . ''","depth":11},{"id":126,"text":"Scalia was the only justice","depth":9},{"id":127,"text":"to suggest","depth":11},{"id":128,"text":"that the speech at issue in the Elonis case `` is not worth a whole lot anyway , ''","depth":11},{"id":129,"text":"regardless of its intent or context .","depth":10},{"id":130,"text":"Justice Kagan , in contrast , seemed to suggest","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"that the government 's position is too broad .","depth":10},{"id":132,"text":"We typically require a kind of buffer zone in First Amendment cases ,","depth":11},{"id":133,"text":"she said ,","depth":11},{"id":134,"text":"to make sure","depth":11},{"id":135,"text":"that `` even stuff","depth":14},{"id":136,"text":"that is wrongful","depth":14},{"id":137,"text":"maybe is permitted","depth":13},{"id":138,"text":"because we do n't want to chill '' the right","depth":13},{"id":139,"text":"to speak freely .","depth":13},{"id":140,"text":"But Dreeben replied","depth":12},{"id":141,"text":"that the rule of law","depth":14},{"id":142,"text":"applied by the lower courts in the Elonis case","depth":14},{"id":143,"text":"is also used in most of the country","depth":13},{"id":144,"text":"and there is `` no evidence ''","depth":12},{"id":145,"text":"anyone 's speech has been chilled .","depth":12},{"id":146,"text":"`` The proof is in the pudding , ''","depth":11},{"id":147,"text":"he contended .","depth":11},{"id":148,"text":"But the justices did n't seem so sure","depth":11},{"id":149,"text":"the pudding","depth":13},{"id":150,"text":"he presented","depth":13},{"id":151,"text":"was to their liking .","depth":12},{"id":152,"text":"Instead , like Goldilocks , they continued to look for a standard","depth":11},{"id":153,"text":"that would be `` just right . ''","depth":11}],"relations":[{"parent":307,"left":155,"right":306,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":155,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":306,"left":183,"right":305,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":183,"left":156,"right":182,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":156,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":182,"left":157,"right":181,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":157,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":181,"left":175,"right":180,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":175,"left":161,"right":174,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":161,"left":6,"right":160,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":160,"left":7,"right":159,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":159,"left":8,"right":158,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":158,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":174,"left":168,"right":173,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":168,"left":162,"right":167,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":162,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":167,"left":13,"right":166,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":166,"left":164,"right":165,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":164,"left":